@asksteph, `statsmodels` released 0.13.0 on Oct 1, which broke a number of things in `sktime` and its dependencies. I see you have it installed.

In the newer development version, we put an upper bound of 0.12.1 on the `statsmodels` requirement - this is perhaps related.
We'll investigate.

